- **Deployment**: The deployment segment includes on-premises and on-demand deployment models. On-premises deployment allows organizations to host and manage the 3D animation software within their own infrastructure, providing them with full control and customization options. On-demand deployment, also known as cloud-based deployment, offers convenience, scalability, and cost-effectiveness by hosting the software on remote servers and providing access through the internet.
